{
  "body": {
    "id": "inclusions01",
    "rows": [
      {
        "id": "header01",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "headercol",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "image",
                "id": "logoimg",
                "values": {
                  "src": {
                    "url": "https://cameronestateinn.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Cameron-Estate-Logo.png",
                    "width": 180,
                    "height": 60,
                    "maxWidth": "50%",
                    "autoWidth": false
                  },
                  "alt": "Cameron Estate Inn",
                  "width": 200,
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "padding": "20px 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#2C3E50",
          "padding": "0 0 0 0"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "opening01",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "opencol01",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "heading",
                "id": "head01",
                "values": {
                  "text": "{{contact.first_name}},",
                  "tag": "h2",
                  "color": "#2C3E50",
                  "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                  "fontSize": 28,
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 10px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text01",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>Here's the thing about wedding planning: there are a lot of line items. Venue rental. Catering minimum. Bar minimum. Cake cutting fee. Coordinator fee. Setup fee. The list goes on.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text02",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>At Cameron Estate, we do things differently. Our pricing is transparent — one price covers almost everything.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#FDFCFA",
          "padding": "40px 40px 20px 40px"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "inclusions01",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "inclcol01",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "heading",
                "id": "head02",
                "values": {
                  "text": "What's Included",
                  "tag": "h2",
                  "color": "#D4AF37",
                  "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                  "fontSize": 24,
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text03",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p><strong>Your choice of ceremony location</strong> — Spring Garden or Conservatory — is included. Cocktail hour space. Your reception ballroom — Spring View Ballroom or Carriage House, depending on your guest count. No separate venue rental fee. No \"facility charge.\" You pay one set price that includes the spaces — no hidden fees.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text04",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p><strong>Tables and chairs</strong> for both ceremony and reception — included. <strong>Premium linens</strong> (tablecloths and napkins) in your choice of colors — included. <strong>Centerpiece vases and table decor elements</strong> — included. Dessert packages available. Cake cutting and service — included. Day of coordinator. Setup crew to transform the spaces according to your vision. Cleanup crew to handle everything after.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text05",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p><strong>Two private changing spaces</strong> provided for the couple to prepare before the ceremony. No need to book a hotel room just for getting ready — we have you covered right here on the estate.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text06",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p><strong>Full plated dinner service</strong> with our experienced culinary team. <strong>Champagne toast</strong> (included in select packages). <strong>Luxury open bar</strong> featuring beer, wine, liquor, and all the mixers. Professional bartenders.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text07",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p><strong>Your dedicated event coordinator</strong> who handles timeline planning, vendor coordination, and day-of management from contract signing to cake cutting. Professional wait staff for your plated dinner service. Bar staff throughout your reception. Setup and cleanup crew.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 20px 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#FFFFFF",
          "padding": "30px 40px 30px 40px"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "cta01",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "ctacol01",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text08",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>We believe in showing you exactly what you'll get — no surprises, no hidden costs. When you come for a tour, I'll walk you through a detailed proposal so you can see exactly where your investment goes.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 25px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "button",
                "id": "btn01",
                "values": {
                  "text": "Schedule Your Private Tour",
                  "href": "{{links.book_tour}}",
                  "backgroundColor": "#D4AF37",
                  "color": "#FFFFFF",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 0 0",
                  "borderRadius": 4
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "sig01",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p style=\"font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500; color: #2C3E50;\">Talk soon,<br/>Lisa</p>",
                  "color": "#2C3E50",
                  "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                  "fontSize": 22,
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "30px 0 0 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#F5F1EB",
          "padding": "40px 40px 20px 40px"
        }
      },
